## Evolution vs. Creationism

* Eugenie C. Scott: [Evolution vs. Creationism: An Introduction](http://www.amazon.com/Evolution-vs-Creationism-An-Introduction/dp/0520246500/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pC_nS_nC?ie=UTF8&colid=1GXBAAITMAONF&coliid=I3USS0AICYVFKG)
* Taner Edis: [Why Intelligent Design Fails: A Scientific Critique of the New Creationism](http://www.amazon.com/Why-Intelligent-Design-Fails-Creationism/dp/081353433X/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pC_nS_nC?ie=UTF8&colid=1GXBAAITMAONF&coliid=I2DW7CU85E33E5)
* Mark Perakh: [Unintelligent Design](http://www.amazon.com/Unintelligent-Design-Mark-Perakh/dp/1591020840/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pC_S_nC?ie=UTF8&colid=1GXBAAITMAONF&coliid=IRWY6OYERAYZA)
* Barbara Forrest: [Creationism's Trojan Horse: The Wedge of Intelligent Design](http://www.amazon.com/Creationisms-Trojan-Horse-Intelligent-Design/dp/0195157427/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pC_S_nC?ie=UTF8&colid=1GXBAAITMAONF&coliid=IZ4QIB19YNYCQ)

